😎 Civic Tech Fest: Call for Papers 😎

TICTeC (The Impacts of Civic Tech Conf) is coming to Taipei 🚀🚀🚀
等不及兩年一次的 g0v summit 了嗎？今年九月，眾星雲集的 Civic Tech Fest 邀稿中!! 快來分享你的開放資料、開放政府、公民科技故事與研究!!
Summit Now >> https://goo.gl/6OT02b

#但g0v不缺超強譯者啦

[Call for Talks, Civic Tech Fest]
The Best-Ever Civic Tech Conf, TICTeC, is coming to Asia!!!
Submit workshop/presentation proposals NOW to share your stories and research!

世界級的公民科技會議即將來台！想第一線加入Civic Tech Fest ? 提交你對於此議題的摘要和工作坊規劃，成為正式參與者！  

◎ 立刻加入 Submit Now >> https://goo.gl/6OT02b

2017 Civic Tech Fest (Sep.11-16) includes：
- TicTec, Taipei
- 2017 World Congress on Information Technology
- Side Events
